1
00:00:31,800 --> 00:00:33,360
Just this scrap metal?

2
00:00:33,630 --> 00:00:35,930
Who are you trying to fool, Ji Qingchen?

3
00:00:36,330 --> 00:00:36,960
Exactly.

4
00:00:37,130 --> 00:00:38,560
You've been the Holy Maiden for so many years.

5
00:00:38,560 --> 00:00:40,330
You must have hoarded the precious treasures

6
00:00:40,330 --> 00:00:41,430
granted by the sect.

7
00:00:41,430 --> 00:00:42,460
Hoarded?

8
00:00:42,530 --> 00:00:44,830
Other than the basic cultivation method given by the sect,

9
00:00:44,830 --> 00:00:47,000
every bit of resource I, Ji Qingchen, used for cultivation,

10
00:00:47,000 --> 00:00:48,260
and every magical artifact I used,

11
00:00:48,260 --> 00:00:49,960
were all earned with my life.

12
00:00:56,800 --> 00:00:58,700
Would the grand senior disciple of Taixuan

13
00:00:58,700 --> 00:00:59,900
be this poor?

14
00:01:00,160 --> 00:01:02,820
Summon the Taixuan Heart-Questioning Mirror.

15
00:01:04,900 --> 00:01:05,459
Even so,

16
00:01:05,630 --> 00:01:07,660
Holy Master, according to sect rules,

17
00:01:07,660 --> 00:01:09,600
since Ji Qingchen insists on leaving the sect,

18
00:01:09,600 --> 00:01:11,260
the sect's cultivation methods she practiced

19
00:01:11,260 --> 00:01:12,500
should be completely abolished.

20
00:01:12,500 --> 00:01:13,860
We absolutely cannot let the Taixuan secret methods

21
00:01:13,860 --> 00:01:15,260
fall into the hands of outsiders.

22
00:01:15,260 --> 00:01:16,760
What a Taixuan Holy Land.

23
00:01:16,800 --> 00:01:18,260
So-called orthodox sect.

24
00:01:18,360 --> 00:01:20,060
It wasn't enough to exploit me for so many years.

25
00:01:20,060 --> 00:01:21,530
Now you want to cripple my cultivation before I leave,

26
00:01:21,530 --> 00:01:22,660
cutting off my livelihood.

27
00:01:22,660 --> 00:01:24,130
I see right through you now.

28
00:01:24,130 --> 00:01:25,530
Fine, I'll cripple it.

29
00:01:27,200 --> 00:01:27,760
Hold on.

30
00:01:28,660 --> 00:01:29,789
That Gu fiend, he...

31
00:01:29,830 --> 00:01:30,400
No.

32
00:01:30,500 --> 00:01:31,360
Master,

33
00:01:31,830 --> 00:01:33,259
is he standing up for me?

34
00:01:33,500 --> 00:01:34,360
Master Gu.

35
00:01:34,759 --> 00:01:36,400
Ji Qingchen crippling her cultivation

36
00:01:36,400 --> 00:01:38,759
is a private matter of our Taixuan Holy Land.

37
00:01:38,759 --> 00:01:39,960
Please do not interfere.

38
00:01:39,960 --> 00:01:40,560
Private matter?

39
00:01:40,560 --> 00:01:41,600
What private matter?

40
00:01:41,600 --> 00:01:42,700
Are you blind?

41
00:01:43,360 --> 00:01:46,800
Didn't you see I just accepted her as my disciple?

42
00:01:47,300 --> 00:01:48,560
My disciple's matter,

43
00:01:48,800 --> 00:01:50,930
you dare tell me it's a private matter?

44
00:02:00,360 --> 00:02:01,560
My disciple

45
00:02:01,760 --> 00:02:05,460
guarded the Heavenly Abyss for your Taixuan Holy Land for so many years.

46
00:02:05,460 --> 00:02:07,160
Not only are you ungrateful,

47
00:02:07,400 --> 00:02:08,960
but you also want to cripple her.

48
00:02:08,960 --> 00:02:10,660
First, tell me,

49
00:02:10,759 --> 00:02:13,530
how does your Taixuan Holy Land plan to compensate her?

50
00:02:13,530 --> 00:02:14,660
Bullshit.

51
00:02:14,660 --> 00:02:17,200
You old fiend, you've only had her as a disciple for less than half an incense stick of time.

52
00:02:17,200 --> 00:02:19,800
What does her guarding the Heavenly Abyss have to do with you?

53
00:02:19,800 --> 00:02:21,660
You clearly just want to take advantage of the situation

54
00:02:21,660 --> 00:02:22,930
and fleece us.

55
00:02:23,560 --> 00:02:25,200
This rebellious disciple, Ji Qingchen,

56
00:02:25,200 --> 00:02:26,660
you can just take her away.

57
00:02:26,900 --> 00:02:27,300
I

58
00:02:27,630 --> 00:02:29,560
won't cripple her cultivation either.

59
00:02:29,560 --> 00:02:31,020
Unwilling to compensate?

60
00:02:31,100 --> 00:02:33,730
Could it be that your Taixuan Holy Land wants something for nothing?

61
00:02:33,730 --> 00:02:37,300
Looking at the entire Xuantian Continent,

62
00:02:37,360 --> 00:02:40,300
it's always been me, Gu Linyuan, bullying others.

63
00:02:40,760 --> 00:02:44,560
Today, your Taixuan Holy Land dares to be so shameless and bullying,

64
00:02:44,800 --> 00:02:46,930
bullying my disciple for being young and ignorant,

65
00:02:46,930 --> 00:02:49,400
actually wanting her to work for hundreds of years for free.

66
00:02:49,400 --> 00:02:50,360
Halberd, come.

67
00:02:53,900 --> 00:02:57,400
If you don't give me and my disciple a satisfactory explanation,

68
00:02:57,400 --> 00:03:01,000
the worst I can do is sink the Central State.

69
00:03:01,860 --> 00:03:03,530
Maniac!

70
00:03:03,660 --> 00:03:04,930
He's a maniac.

71
00:03:05,260 --> 00:03:06,900
Who takes an Extreme Dao Emperor Weapon

72
00:03:06,900 --> 00:03:09,060
with them on a stroll?

73
00:03:09,060 --> 00:03:11,200
Aren't these things usually kept deep in the ancestral land

74
00:03:11,200 --> 00:03:13,360
to suppress the foundation and destiny?

75
00:03:13,360 --> 00:03:15,500
This cheap master is so domineering.

76
00:03:15,800 --> 00:03:19,360
But it feels great to be protected without reservation.

77
00:03:19,360 --> 00:03:21,130
Master Gu, don't be impulsive.

78
00:03:21,200 --> 00:03:23,300
Let's talk this out.

79
00:03:23,300 --> 00:03:25,700
I said this guy is a maniac,

80
00:03:25,800 --> 00:03:27,600
an unforgivable fiend.

81
00:03:27,730 --> 00:03:29,000
Billions of lives in the Central State,

82
00:03:29,000 --> 00:03:30,600
and he says he'll sink them.

83
00:03:38,500 --> 00:03:40,160
Extreme Dao Emperor's might.

84
00:03:40,660 --> 00:03:44,030
Who is the Taixuan Holy Land going to war with?

85
00:03:48,430 --> 00:03:49,360
What's going on?

86
00:03:49,530 --> 00:03:51,630
The Emperor Weapon awakened on its own.

87
00:03:51,630 --> 00:03:54,290
Did a Supreme from the Forbidden Zone attack us?

88
00:03:54,730 --> 00:03:56,329
Taixuan is in danger.

89
00:03:58,130 --> 00:03:58,829
Today,

90
00:03:59,260 --> 00:04:02,630
your Taixuan Holy Land must give me an explanation.

91
00:04:03,630 --> 00:04:05,230
Otherwise, if word gets out,

92
00:04:05,730 --> 00:04:09,000
people will think I, Gu Linyuan, am easy to bully.

93
00:04:09,030 --> 00:04:10,660
Fellow Daoist, please wait.

94
00:04:21,130 --> 00:04:23,190
Just because of this trivial matter.

95
00:04:23,400 --> 00:04:25,600
I thought a mortal enemy was attacking.

96
00:04:25,860 --> 00:04:29,300
I wasted a top-grade divine source for extending life.

97
00:04:30,660 --> 00:04:32,700
I really want to give these unworthy descendants

98
00:04:32,700 --> 00:04:34,430
a big slap in the face.

99
00:04:35,200 --> 00:04:36,400
Fellow Daoist.

100
00:04:38,260 --> 00:04:39,520
You are not qualified.

101
00:04:41,700 --> 00:04:43,159
Let Li Taixuan come.

102
00:04:43,330 --> 00:04:44,530
So damn shameless.

103
00:04:44,600 --> 00:04:46,730
Li Taixuan is the real name of our Taixuan Emperor,

104
00:04:46,730 --> 00:04:49,200
who passed away tens of thousands of years ago.

105
00:04:49,200 --> 00:04:50,430
If the Emperor were still alive,

106
00:04:50,430 --> 00:04:52,200
you wouldn't be so arrogant.

107
00:04:53,030 --> 00:04:54,600
You must be joking.

108
00:04:55,400 --> 00:04:58,659
Our Taixuan Holy Emperor is willing to compensate.

109
00:05:00,430 --> 00:05:03,160
Please put away the Emperor Weapon first.

110
00:05:03,460 --> 00:05:04,530
Oh.
